## Analytics

Track engagement with the comparison page by:

1. Adding event tracking to CTAs:
```typescript
onClick={() => {
  // Track event
  analytics.track('comparison_cta_clicked', {
    destination: '/docs'
  });
}}
```

2. Adding scroll depth tracking:
```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  const handleScroll = () => {
    const scrollPercent = (window.scrollY / (document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight)) * 100;
    if (scrollPercent > 50) {
      analytics.track('comparison_page_scrolled');
    }
  };
  window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);
  return () => window.removeEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);
}, []);
```

